;※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※
;Custom dialogue settings, custom code
;※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※
;made it as a way to speed up the update process and separate simple flag updates from various customization options
@KOJO_OPTION_EXIST_K1
#LOCALSIZE 1
#LOCALSSIZE 1
;note: options start from 1!
@KOJO_OPTION_K1
#LOCALSIZE 1
#LOCALSSIZE 1
CALL KOJO_OPTION_ITEM("切换同框架剧本", 1, "status:初始版:无个性版", CFLAG:1:998)
CALL KOJO_OPTION_ITEM("启用个（人）性（癖）内容", 2, "status:OFF:ON", GETBIT(CFLAG:1:1500, 0))

;process the input portion
@KOJO_OPTION_K1_RESULT_1
CFLAG:1:口上セレクタ = 1

@KOJO_OPTION_K1_RESULT_2
;sets CFLAG:1500
;bit 0: Controls if content should be shown
;bit 1: If set to 0, this function will be called when first selecting COM180 with Reimu
VARSET LOCAL
LOCAL = LINECOUNT
$LOOPSTART
CLEARLINE LINECOUNT - LOCAL
PRINTDL 虽然很唐突、但是你能接受恋物癖么？
PRINTDL ※没有什么特殊意图哦～※
CALL ASK_M(LOCAL:1?"我他妈选爆"#"是", 1, LOCAL:1?"端下去吧"#"否", 1, "请给我解释一下", 1, "保留", SELECTCOM == 180 ? -1 # 1)

SELECTCASE RESULT
	CASE 0
		PRINTFORMDL 选择了【\@ LOCAL:1 ? 我他妈选爆 # 是 \@】
			CFLAG:1:1500 = 3
	CASE 1
		PRINTFORMDL 选择了【\@ LOCAL:1 ? 端下去吧 # 否 \@】
			CFLAG:1:1500 = 2
	CASE 2
		PRINTDW 只是狂舔灵梦的脚而已。
		LOCAL:1 = 1
		GOTO LOOPSTART
	CASE 3
		PRINTFORMDW 暂且保留，返回上级菜单
			CFLAG:1:1500 = 0
		RETURN
	ENDSELECT
PRINTFORMDW 冒昧打扰了、那么、请继续享受和灵梦的性活吧……

RETURN 1

;※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※※
;"ENCOUNTER"系イベント（エクストラ构文）
